The paper discusses online learning algorithms and their performance in various settings, including convex optimization and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
